\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Surfer SEO stood out by being the only one to send a plain text dunning email\'97and honestly, it worked.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li800\fi-800\ri800\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \uc0\u55357 \u56481  The message came directly from a real person, with no flashy design or branding, just a simple, human note explaining that my payment of $106.80 didn\'92t go through. The email included a friendly request to update my payment information and a soft \'93we\'92ll give it another try.\'94 No harsh language, no panic\'97just clear, calm communication.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 It felt personal, not automated, which builds trust. For a dunning email, that plain-text format was refreshingly real and surprisingly effective.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
