\cf0 \strokec2 \uc0\u55357 \u56481  The tone is warm and relaxed\'97they even say \'93put your feet up and relax\'94 while they retry the payment. That small touch of humor goes a long way in keeping the customer relationship intact. The second message outlines exactly what happens if payment isn\'92t resolved, including a downgrade to the free plan with feature limits.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 It\'92s transparent, helpful, and easy to act on. Overall, Buffer does a great job reminding customers without sounding robotic or pushy.\
